narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes. Good lab class. Not too much worth throughout the semester. Fun. And informative.

This lab was pretty fun as we were a small group and actually got to know each other and the professor and TA. Also, for the most part the labs were rarely simply "Run a test and wait" that wasted our time. All of our projects had legitimate products. That doesn't mean there wasn't an obscene lab report, but everything else was fairly reasonable.
